# LVINIT environment variables
# Copy the ones you need into your Vercel project (Settings → Environment
# Variables). Nothing here is required to run the site — the contact form
# falls back to a mailto draft and analytics simply stays off until set.

# --- Contact form (Resend) ---
# Create a key at https://resend.com and verify your sending domain (lvinit.com)
# so mail can send from hello@lvinit.com.
RESEND_API_KEY=
# Verified sender. Must be on a domain you've verified in Resend.
CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL="LVINIT <hello@lvinit.com>"
# Where leads are delivered (defaults to hello@lvinit.com if unset).
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=hello@lvinit.com

# --- Analytics (Google Analytics 4) ---
# Your GA4 Measurement ID, e.g. G-XXXXXXXXXX. Leave blank to keep analytics off.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=
